		"description": "Complete API collection for WriteWave Progress Service with automated testing, environment management, and comprehensive examples.\n\n## Features\n- ✅ Automated test scripts for all endpoints\n- ✅ Auto token management\n- ✅ Variable extraction from responses\n- ✅ Comprehensive request/response examples\n- ✅ Pre-request scripts for dynamic values\n\n## Quick Start\n1. Set `accessToken` variable (get from user-service login)\n2. Set `userId` variable or use auto-generated test user\n3. Start with Health Check endpoint\n4. All endpoints include automated tests\n\n## Collection Variables\n- `baseUrl`: http://localhost:8003/api/v1\n- `userId`: User ID for testing (auto-generated if not set)\n- `accessToken`: JWT token for authentication\n- `characterId`: Character ID for practice (auto-generated if not set)",
